description:
Madhouse Escape v1.0 full

If you are not afraid to get lost in the depths of your mind and madness, then welcome to the madhouse a place where you submit reality or reality hold you. For each new door you will find a way to get out of the world generated by sick mind.

- Interesting puzzles and tasks;
- Realistic graphics and sound effects;
- Different themes of each level;

Recently seen on mobile platforms the dominance of simple and unpretentious quests with scenes and gameplay similar to each other like two drops of water. Of course, this situation can not to upset fans of the genre. However, sometimes there are also quite worthy representatives of the genre, such as the Escape Madhouse.
Madhouse or the Escape Escape from the psychiatric hospital â€“ classic quest with a familiar game mechanics and intuitive controls, everything is without surprises. But here on the story and the gameplay is more detail. It is not difficult to guess from the title you have to escape from a closed psychiatric institution, which of course will affect what you see and hear, do not trust their feelings. Be bold and move forward. Graphics also perfectly conveys the atmosphere of despair and hopelessness.

By Night Owls Group

Requires Android 2.3 and up
